{"tid":1392606,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#AOC #Ageofempires #新戰略 #打技術性防守","createTime":"2019-07-31T20:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:59:17.000Z","uid":225002,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8296711fff27e0b05085ba23072edadf8939fbc","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://store-images.s-microsoft.com/image/apps.35730.13954787087416189.9666adfa-59c2-4b87-b126-9798005cd1d0.45144e9b-e154-4b4e-a32f-891934c8c0d7?w=672&amp;h=378&amp;q=80&amp;mode=letterbox&amp;background=%23FFE4E4E4&amp;format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore-images.s-microsoft.com%2Fimage%2Fapps.35730.13954787087416189.9666adfa-59c2-4b87-b126-9798005cd1d0.45144e9b-e154-4b4e-a32f-891934c8c0d7%3Fw%3D672%26h%3D378%26q%3D80%26mode%3Dletterbox%26background%3D%2523FFE4E4E4%26format%3Djpg&h=b26b09bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇片睇人打match，睇到D速畜直接charge去條防線，而防線只係好靜態咁用盾用罩去擋，D人仲要企到密密麻麻，條防線仲要真嘅，最後潰散收場。我睇到好心痛，所以謀劃了以下改良方案。<br />\n<br />\n1. D人企到密密麻麻，第一線想向後退兩步都退唔到。老實講，唔應該企到咁密，應該一排排咁企，令排與排之間有活動空間，第一排想退嘅時候，第二排頂上，或者，第一排走唔到嘅時候，第二排立即撲上偷雞，如是者，連第二排都頂唔住嘅時候，第三四排撲上。不要畏懼，人數是力量。<br />\n<br />\n2. 條防線係唔應該係直嘅，而係應該兩翼突出+中間向內凹，好似一條內曲線咁，形成進攻者容易被防線兩翼包餃子嘅陣勢。當然，兩翼就好可能變左做磁石吸攻擊，所以：1. 最強嘅人做兩翼 2. 兩翼受壓，中間就要主動向外突擊。同上，不要畏懼，人數是力量。<br />\n<br />\n3. 成功嘅防守唔應該係完全靜態，完全比對方掌握到節奏同動態，最終只會導致失敗。要不斷輸出騷擾，不斷輸出壓力，咁對方嘅進攻部隊先會出錯。唔係嘅話對方係會越打越順，咁你就收皮嘅啦。<br />\n<br />\n4. 最好嘅防禦，唔係盾唔係罩，而係拒馬。盾/罩係平嘅，唔會對佢地構成任何危險，所以佢地會好勇。但前線何來拒馬？馬其頓方陣咪係囉，一排由長矛構成嘅移動拒馬。唔好開罩，會擋住視線，無左視線你就越係驚，應該收起佢當長矛用。可參考Bravebeart嘅一幕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QULj7MecgaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQULj7MecgaQ&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGJj7jGrzIfagxCK2eNaONkM%3D&h=6b17c321\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QULj7MecgaQ</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 活動空間同視線好重要，所以我要開多一個point 來講。活動空間同視線好重要，可以嘅話盡量唔好開遮，唔好企咁逼。<br />\n<br />\nPS：只要你生擒到一隻速畜(打rush嘅畜生)，一隻咁多，就破左速畜嘅金面罩嘅啦。"},{"pid":"2c5e9d8e9ad5b391d63d1e3fb70542d9c7a05ed5","tid":1392606,"uid":264398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"339d07046e0c46ff213f7e3393ba8b81c7caed63","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51a6d5ca40d2d007b2c0f6aa2c25226908719590","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0b020093da1d10fcf9836abb83068dd9f1aaf8a","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a6d5ca40d2d007b2c0f6aa2c25226908719590","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e76f507b116826dfe846972d42281a4e674b7446","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2aa3b6d0083d55cd8f00afbd049d330653ddf9b9","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仆你臭街，比d反應呀威！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8c0c60b10bfc5610d2c34e93ee4d49259e4250bb","tid":1392606,"uid":287206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f41ffea18b8c7228168f2839c31fb5cc8056abd4","tid":1392606,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff650046b63686f973e9b97c07167f4dff635175","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"nice!"},{"pid":"5793521274e64ecad56fbd5d97aa2494450c5ce5","tid":1392606,"uid":225002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim